# Smart Step Website - Environment Variables

# ==============================================================================
# GEMINI API KEY (REQUIRED)
# ==============================================================================
# Google Gemini API key for AI-powered translation features
# Get your API key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# This is used by the useAutoTranslation hook for automatic content translation
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ==============================================================================
# BACKEND API CONFIGURATION (Optional for frontend-only development)
# ==============================================================================
# If you're running the Laravel backend, these are already configured in vite.config.ts
# The frontend proxies /api and /sanctum requests to http://localhost:8000
# No additional configuration needed unless you change the backend port

# Note: The backend should be running on port 8000 for the proxy to work
# See backend/README.md for backend setup instructions
